OL,3,CManchester Airport to remove barriers
OL,4,Cat pick-up and drop-off zones
OL,6,FManchester Airport is to remove the
OL,7,Fbarriers at the exits to the pick-up
OL,8,Fand drop-off zones and replace them
OL,9,Fwith a new barrierless system.
OL,11,FWork to remove the barriers will take
OL,12,Fplace between Wednesday 26 March and
OL,13,FWednesday 2 April.
OL,15,FThe Airport says the switch to a new
OL,16,Fbarrierless drop-off and pick-up
OL,17,Fsystem will improve the overall
OL,18,Fexperience for both drivers and
OL,19,Fpassengers by streamlining the process.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
