OL,3,CManchester Airport to remove barriers
OL,4,Cat pick-up and drop-off zones
OL,6,FThe Airport claims by removing the
OL,7,Fexisting barriers, drivers will pass
OL,8,Fthrough more smoothly without the need
OL,9,Fto stop on exit, helping reduce
OL,10,Fcongestion and helping people avoid
OL,11,Fincreased charges as a result of
OL,12,Fhaving to wait to leave the zones.
OL,14,FThe new technology will be managed
OL,15,Fthrough an automatic number plate
OL,16,Frecognition (ANPR) system like that
OL,17,Falready in use at some other UK
OL,18,Fairports and familiar settings like
OL,19,Fbridges and tunnels.
