OL,3,CManchester Airport to remove barriers
OL,4,Cat pick-up and drop-off zones
OL,6,FCameras will identify cars by their
OL,7,Fregistration number and automatically
OL,8,Frecord who has used the pick-up or
OL,9,Fdrop-off zone.
OL,11,FRather than stopping at a barrier and
OL,12,Fpaying as they leave the area, drivers
OL,13,Fwill leave and then pay the charge by
OL,14,Fmidnight the following day.
OL,16,FThey can do this online or over the
OL,17,Fphone.
