OL,3,CManchester Airport to remove barriers
OL,4,Cat pick-up and drop-off zones
OL,6,FThe barrierless system will be in
OL,7,Fplace at the pick-up and drop-off
OL,8,Fzones in all three of the airport's
OL,9,Fterminals as well as it the train,
OL,10,Ftram and bus station.
OL,12,FThe new system will go live in a
OL,13,Fphased approach at each location
OL,14,Fbetween 26 March and 2 April.
OL,16,FSigns on approach to each zone will
OL,17,Fadvise people of the steps they need
OL,18,Fto take.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
