OL,3,CManchester Airport to remove barriers
OL,4,Cat pick-up and drop-off zones
OL,6,FThere will be no change to the
OL,7,Fexisting charges. No payments will be
OL,8,Fmade when exiting theJzones.
OL,10,FOnce a driver has used a zone they
OL,11,Fwill have until midnight the next day
OL,12,Fto pay. Frequent users, including taxi
OL,13,Fdrivers, will be able to set up an
OL,14,Fauto-pay account.
OL,16,FBoth the phone line and the website
OL,17,Ffor paying the charges will go live
OL,18,Fshortly before the barriers are
OL,19,Fremoved and will be clearly signposted
OL,20,Fat the zones.
